{"data":[{"date":"21:40 15/08","title":"Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd thua \"b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng\" c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chu-nha-olympic-indonesia-bat-ngo-thua-bai-tuong-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 ba b\u1ea3ng A, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 18 ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi &ldquo;ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda&rdquo; Patriot Chandrabhaga, Indonesia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Milla Luis c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i l\u00ean Palestine, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 18. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u0110\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua 16 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZulfiandi ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Darwish Mohamed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11 m. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Dabbagh Oday \u0111\u00e3 mang ni\u1ec1m vui v\u1ec1 cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Sandouqa Ayman.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic Palestine 1-2 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic Palestine 1-2 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/palestine-indonesia-2120207.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Olympic Indonesia (\u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf) thua Olympic Palestine.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, Indonesia d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 7 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 V\u1ea1n \u0110\u1ea3o qu\u00e2n b\u00ecnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Jaya Irfan tho\u00e1t b\u1ea9y b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mamada Rami b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. C\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Palestine l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Sandouqa Ayman c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn 45 ph\u00fat kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Trung \u0110\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Darwish Mohamed tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1, n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 51.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng t\u1ef1 \u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Indonesia. H\u1ecd li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed3n \u00e9p v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-2 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Hong Kong b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan (Trung Qu\u1ed1c) t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi leo l\u00ean ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng A. Hai c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Tarres Paramo Jorge (9&rsquo;, 41&rsquo;) v\u00e0 Tan Chun Lok (5&rsquo;, 37&rsquo;) \u0111\u00e3 mang ni\u1ec1m vui cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Kwok Kar Lok Kenneth.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, Olympic Palestine t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Trung \u0110\u00f4ng 1 tr\u1eadn, Hong Kong (6 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia (3 \u0111i\u1ec3m) l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t x\u1ebfp c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 ba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y 17/8, trong khi Indonesia ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng L\u00e0o, th\u00ec Hong Kong ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Palestine.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang bang A sau luot tran ngay 15/8.\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng A sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ng\u00e0y 15/8.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/cats.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng A sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ng\u00e0y 15/8.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/ngoi-sao-son-heung-min-du-bi-olympic-han-quoc-van-thang-tennis-o-asiad-2018-472-194561.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn th\u1eafng tennis \u1edf Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-malaysia-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-o-asiad-18-472-194553.html\">Olympic Malaysia kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 \u1edf Asiad 18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong-168-194537.html\">Th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2409","checkdouble":"194562"},{"date":"22:01 15/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/tan-binh-arsenal-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-vo-dich-cua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier League 2018/19 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u00f5 n\u00e9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Man City hay Liverpool, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u0103ng quang Premier League \u00edt nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/193635-sao-tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Guendouzi t\u1ef1 tin Arsenal v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Matteo Guendouzi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c bi quan nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n t\u1ef1 tinh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, t\u00e2n binh \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf Emirates v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u00f4i tin Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 xem. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ea1nh tranh cho danh hi\u1ec7u ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-truoc-mua-giai-201819-su-tro-lai-cua-chu-tu-172-193956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/Arsenal-giu-chan-Ramsey-Vi-chuyen-mon-va-mot-loi-khang-dinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-truoc-mua-giai-201819-su-tro-lai-cua-chu-tu-172-193956.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ch\u00fa T\u01b0</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi, hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi sau 22 n\u0103m th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u00ecm ngh\u1ec9m d\u1ea7n d\u00e0. Tr\u00e1i ng\u1ecdt th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2408","checkdouble":"194563"},{"date":"22:26 15/08","title":"Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/sao-man-utd-tri-an-mourinho-sau-khi-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce quy k\u1ebft b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thua-cua-arsenal-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 dung th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng pressing xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 y nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Arsenal tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2 reo khi Petr Cech quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sang ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9. Khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Man City r\u1ed3i anh mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec th\u00ec l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2407","checkdouble":"194564"},{"date":"23:00 15/08","title":"Sao Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/sao-arsenal-tu-sanh-minh-voi-ronaldo-va-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cGia nh\u1eadp Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho t\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec trong s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u x\u00e1n l\u1ea1n cho t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/aubameyang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, c\u00e1i \u201ckh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Gabon c\u1ee7a Dortmund n\u00f3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi nhanh nh\u01b0 ch\u1edbp, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi anh ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea5y Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i thu th\u1eadp s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Salah \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y r\u1ea5t nhanh r\u1ed3i c\u01a1 m\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch xem nh\u1eefng b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh ghi l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cN\u0103m nay trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 37km/h v\u00e0 ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Mbappe \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 29, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/3/goc-arsenal-thanh-hinh-voi-aubameyang-va-nhung-van-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Aubameyang v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon, nh\u01b0ng song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi bi\u1ebft bao h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2406","checkdouble":"194565"},{"date":"23:39 15/08","title":"Man Utd \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/man-utd-don-day-du-trong-phao-tro-lai-cuoi-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u00eam hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p hai v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t v\u00f4 duy\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jesse Lingard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Pogba, Rashford v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, Lukaku, Lingard v\u00e0 Fellaini c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2405","checkdouble":"194567"},{"date":"23:54 15/08","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/tan-hlv-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-hoc-doi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce quy k\u1ebft b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thua-cua-arsenal-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 dung th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng pressing xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 y nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Arsenal tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2 reo khi Petr Cech quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sang ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9. Khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Man City r\u1ed3i anh mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec th\u00ec l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2404","checkdouble":"194568"},{"date":"00:24 16/08","title":"Man City nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 De Bruyne","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/Kevin-De-Bruyne-1003773.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00ec Kevin De Bruyne v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Manchester City v\u00e0 theo nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ra t\u1eeb Etihad, c\u00e1c C\u0110V s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u n\u1eefa m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Kevin-De-Bruyne-1003773.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 theo chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Kristof Terreur, c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu nguy c\u01a1 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, Man City s\u1ebd t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, De Bruyne s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 League Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/10 g\u1eb7p Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Man City tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, De Bruyne ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Man City v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi bi\u1ebft bao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao-172-171225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/21/kevin-de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao-172-171225.html\">Kevin De Bruyne: T\u1eeb th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c \u01b0\u01a1ng b\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ai bi\u1ebft Kevin De Bruyne t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e0n anh David Silva hay Fernandinho, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u01b0\u1eddi x\u00f2a r\u1ed3i n\u00f3i: Th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2403","checkdouble":"194571"},{"date":"00:52 16/08","title":"Ramos ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/ramos-phan-phao-ronaldo-de-bao-ve-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh d\u00e0nh cho Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t d\u00ecm h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a CR7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt tai trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ed1n c\u0169 Real Madrid v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/ramos-phan-phao-ronaldo-de-bao-ve-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ea7m hi\u1ec3u qua nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf th\u00e0nh Turin c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i khi Juventus l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Italia c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c b\u1edfi n\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c cho t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Ronaldo c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u1edf Bernabeu, n\u01a1i anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra kh\u00f4ng \u00edt m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1eeb HLV \u0111\u1ebfn ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a CR7 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nghe ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed5i anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 ra sao, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng Ronaldo. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u1ebft, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ai mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Real Madrid vs Atletico 02h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Atletico: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real vs Atletico Madrid Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2402","checkdouble":"194572"},{"date":"00:52 16/08","title":"Olympic Myanmar su\u00fdt \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-myanmar-suyt-danh-bai-chdcnd-trieu-tien-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng, g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Iran, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Olympic Myanmar v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, khi c\u1ea7m ho\u00e0 CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean 1-1, trong th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Do n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Iran, CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia, n\u00ean Myanmar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u201ct\u1eed th\u1ea7n\u201d n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, Myanmar th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 k\u1ebft th\u00fac 1 ph\u00fat, Myanmar c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n. Sau 3 \u2013 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi nhau, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Maung Maung Lwin, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u00fat c\u0103ng t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng 18m, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kang Ju Hyok c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc \u00c1, gi\u00fap Myanmar b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u1eabn 1-0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Myanmar kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPh\u00fat 60, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Htet Kyaw Zin va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Myanmar trong khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh. Thay v\u00ec nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u1eeba n\u00eau b\u00ean ph\u00eda Myanmar l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y v\u1eeba g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Myanmar, v\u1eeba khi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao b\u1eaft vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb, m\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i th\u1ea5p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh, khi\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00e1p s\u00e1t c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Myanmar.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, r\u1ed3i Kim Yu Song b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc \u00c1, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Htet Kyaw Zin b\u00ean ph\u00eda Myanmar, \u0111\u1ec3 Jang Kuk Chol ung dung \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng, g\u1ee1 ho\u00e0 1-1 cho CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u1eadn ho\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi\u1ebfn Myanmar m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F, b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ea3ng, Iran ho\u00e0 Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2401","checkdouble":"194574"},{"date":"06:46 16/08","title":"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u vinh quang nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>HLV Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Atletico Madrid m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ngo\u00e0i ra, chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap HLV Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Atletico.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c HLV gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \"El Cholo\" \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 7 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Luis Aragones (6). HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (2012, 2018), 2 Europa League, 1 La Liga, 1 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua v\u00e0 1 Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t HLV Simeone c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League danh gi\u00e1. El Cholo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Atletico hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 2016 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Simeone c\u0169ng l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua, Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>G\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 nh\u01b0ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eeba n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Los Blancos thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng sau Bernd Schuster n\u0103m 2007.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Julen Lopetegui c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n n\u1eefa khi tr\u1edf HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec3 thua 4 b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 60 n\u0103m. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf Real Madrid l\u00e0 Michael Keeping trong tr\u1eadn thua Celta Vigo.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc-172-194531.html\">Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-atletico-madrid-01-inter-milan-icc-2018-329-194290.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Atletico Madrid 0-1 Inter Milan (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2400","checkdouble":"194576"},{"date":"14:05 15/08","title":"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng L'Equipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u lung lay do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p\u00a0BL\u0110\u00a0Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, th\u00ec Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/zidane-den-mu-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" \u1edf MU m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00f3ng th\u1ebf\" Benitez v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi Real trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm HLV\u00a0m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng Zizou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Zidane (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Ancelotti \u1edf Bernabeu). K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \"Zizou \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebf\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Real ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh h\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u00e0 Zidane t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zidane, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 L\u0110B\u0110 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng m\u1eddi HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd L'Equire, Zidane l\u1ea1i h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd do thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, MU g\u1eb7p may khi th\u1eafng Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. V\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, \u0111\u01b0a vinh quang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho, MU ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool-172-194512.html\">M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-194468.html\">Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2399","checkdouble":"194534"},{"date":"14:21 15/08","title":"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chan-sut-son-heungmin-canh-bao-dong-doi-truoc-them-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan t\u1ea1i ASIAD&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau khi anh v\u1eeba c\u00f9ng Tottenham gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 sau khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Tuy v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham bay th\u1eb3ng sang T\u00e2y Java t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ngay sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Newcastle.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Son Heung-min nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Chan-sut-Son-Heung-min-nhac-nho-dong-doi-truoc-them-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-Min mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea5m HCV 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Son Heung-min c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Ui-Jo c\u1ee7a Gamba Osaka v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jo Hyeon-Woo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Anh v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i xem m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ea1 \u1edf World Cup, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y&rdquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do s\u1edbm c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Indonesia, Son Heung-min cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 ASIAD tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cho h\u1ecd l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn h\u1ecd c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min t\u1edbi v\u1edbi ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Theo lu\u1eadt H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ecdi nam c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tu\u1ed5i 27 song v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh HCV ch\u00e2u \u00c1 hay Olympic.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2398","checkdouble":"194535"},{"date":"15:00 15/08","title":"Th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m th\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Truong\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/thong-tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-xuan-truong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL b\u1ecb \u0111au \u1edf ch\u00e2n l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m - Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch th\u00eam v\u00ec l\u00fd do thay Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi&nbsp;HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, so v\u1edbi Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park tung H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t &quot;s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda&quot; gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-canh-giac-truoc-cac-doi-bong-o-bang-d-168-194534.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho &lsquo;\u0111\u00e0n em&rsquo; C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2397","checkdouble":"194537"},{"date":"15:07 15/08","title":"Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng L'Equipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Man Utd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t thay t\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u lung lay do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p\u00a0BL\u0110\u00a0Man Utd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, th\u00ec Zidane s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU h\u00e8 2018 Zidane s\u1ebd thay Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/zidane-den-mu-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn \"gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\" \u1edf MU m\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u00f3ng th\u1ebf\" Benitez v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ban \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi Real trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm HLV\u00a0m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng Zizou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m HLV\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Zidane (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafm vai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd cho HLV Ancelotti \u1edf Bernabeu). K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \"Zizou \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebf\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Zidane b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Real ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh h\u1ed3i g\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u00e0 Zidane t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Zidane, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 L\u0110B\u0110 Qatar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng m\u1eddi HLV 46 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng theo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb t\u1edd L'Equire, Zidane l\u1ea1i h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Old Trafford trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd do thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. Ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, MU g\u1eb7p may khi th\u1eafng Leicester 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c, Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League 2018/19. V\u00e0 Zidane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, \u0111\u01b0a vinh quang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho, MU ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 cho HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool-172-194512.html\">M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca-172-194472.html\">MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Pogba cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ander-herrera-goi-y-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-mu-172-194468.html\">Ander Herrera mang tin vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/darmian-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu-172-194460.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2396","checkdouble":"194539"},{"date":"15:33 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 14/8 v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. N\u1ebfu C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/olympic-viet-nam-vs-pakistan-8-153424042905491724090.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho \u0110T\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Sportalkorea\u00a0\u0111\u01b0a tin: Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd Chosun l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8: \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi sang ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\">Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2395","checkdouble":"194540"}]}